title: Colin Cowherd's Blazing 5: 12/08/2018

description:
Coming off another disappointing week Colin tries to rebound and gives his Blazing 5 picks from week 14 to RJ Bell of Pregame.com and Fox Sports Radio who tells him which ones the wise guys in Vegas agree with. Plus, Colin releases a special bonus pick that was not included in his Blazing 5.
